    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Boards upon which one writes directly, usually of a size larger than handheld. For smaller board-like objects for writing, use "writing tablets (writing equipment)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
